content:
                I had a little cow;
                Hey-diddle, ho-diddle!
        I had a little cow, and it had a little calf,
        Hey-diddle, ho-diddle; and there's my song half.

                I had a little cow;
                Hey-diddle, ho-diddle!
        I had a little cow, and I drove it to the stall;
        Hey-diddle, ho-diddle; and there's my song all!
